metadata.name: Soul Globe #01
metadata.description:
Soul Globe #01

The first Globe of the collection is filled with sun, blue skies and the sound of a Mediterranean afternoon. Enjoy the warmth!


About the Soul Globe Collection:

Our souls are much larger than our egos. Soul Globes give the visitor a view at their inner lives, contemplating the continuous change of moods and emotions, colours and sounds.

Find the Globe that speaks to you and enjoy the journey!


Purchaser will get original file:

2000 x 2000 Pixels
00:57 Loop
QT movie 1.16 GB
Apple ProRes 422
Stereo Audio 44.1 kHz
